data.description:
Gorgeous Modular Rustic Ranch (see hud info in private remarks), on 1.85 acres, beautifully located in Howard about 12 miles from Salida off of Hwy 50. Beautiful river-front drive from Howard to Salida. Very well kept, non smoker home. No home owner association or any type of monetary community expenses. Home comes with Blue Ribbon Warranty (renewable by Buyer)
1682 sq ft  3 bedroom, 2 full baths. Master bedroom bath includes a jack and jill hot tub along with a separate shower walk-in.  Ranch home sits on 1.85 access with an panoramic view of the Mountains as you walk out the front door. Back porch view allows overlook of Arkansas river and valley. Quiet neighborhood allows for walks in view of the close-by mountains and forests.  House sits on a mountain plateau that is fairly level. Circular driveway at end of cul-de-sac.  Separate two car garage, double doors, remote controlled, with bonus room attached (can be used as workshop, has been paneled).  Garage contains built-in air compressor overhead with hose connections on ground level.  House has 3 set of covered porches, including ramp access for elderly and infirm. Beautiful path walk between home and garage, lined with rock, with fence yard.  Huge kitchen area with separate walk-in laundry room. House floor plan is a split bedroom plan.  All appliances stay except refrigerator and washer and dryer. Composite roofing.
Road to house is publicly maintained year around. No easement issues. Additional Outside storage shed between Home and Garage.
DO NOT MISS THE 45 DIGITAL PICTURES OF SURROUNDING BEAUTY OF THE HOME.(click once and all 45 will rotate through)
